tasks.task: Preparing spray liquid for pesticide application
subtasks: Rinse measuring cylinder three times
Add rinse water to spray liquid
If pesticide containers emptied, rinse them with water
Add pesticide container rinses to sprayer tank
Repeat rinse and add steps two more times
Replace sprayer tank lid
Agitate sprayer to mix product and water
Visit website for more info on pesticide use and Personal Protective Equipment (PPE)

subtasks: Rinse the measuring cylinder three times and add water to the spray liquid

tasks.task: Preparing spray liquid for pesticide application
subtasks: Rinse the measuring cylinder three times and add this water to the spray liquid
If you have emptied any pesticide containers, also rinse them with water and add the rinsing water into the sprayer tank (repeat this process two more times)
Replace the tank lid
Agitate the sprayer to mix the product with the water.
